                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The pridespawn sentinel stumbles back and appears frightened and intimidated by a creature within 30 feet that it can see. The targeted creature must attempt a @Check[will|dc:32] save; regardless of the result, that creature is temporarily immune to False Pride for 24 hours.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature becomes overconfident and careless as they believe themselves to be more intimidating than they actually are. They're @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] against the next attack the pridespawn sentinel attempts against them this round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, but the creature's false pride causes them to become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round as they spend one of their actions posturing and bragging about their superiority. They're off-guard as long as they remain slowed.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but for 1 minute.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
